# {.title-slide .centeredslide background-iframe="https://saforem2.github.io/grid-worms-animation/" loading="lazy"}

Centered Slides
We can center all the text on a slide by adding the {.centeredslide} class to the slide header, e.g.

index.qmdstyle.scss


---
format:
  revealjs:
    theme: [style.scss]
---

# Title {.centeredslide}


.centeredslide {
  text-align: center;
}
